{"tid":1549383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日和平！衝既即刻制止 打殘！感謝各位","createTime":"2019-09-07T09:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T10:05:05.000Z","uid":192957,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"582c91ab34ac2b6a639def0c5f19097114fd70d7","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:53:00.000Z","msg":"聽日不反對通知書已批！<br />\n <strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住聽日係去求人 唔該提提無玩開連登既手足 我地要和平 禮貌。</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n一有人衝 大家幫手制止。9成係狗 所以點做呢。。就自己諗啦。<br />\n<br />\n另外我地可以寫定信去美領 話會有黑警扮普通人衝擊<br />\n1. 聽日幾點邊到 我地既目的<br />\n2. 提醒聽日可能做有黑警搞事<br />\n3. 以之前黑警扮示威者作例子<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位香港人！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avzmpdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavzmpdW.png&h=def86c85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e05ab2913c3df28429d06bf1502fcf2bdc1f640","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"bba9b2915d487dcdba35bfbeff301138003f6f88","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"cf6976f78ade3463fd5ad315bd737a8a035bd199","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"19daf06c4107d17310fafb516e019ff1d643948c","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"f7ab69a688f7fd6b79f9d8c34b3965335902371d","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1b6c97be3d7083d1de99aff4bfd72f9bdc44f83f","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1079e5794500c371411d7d230b543c6890d1abb7","tid":1549383,"uid":192957,"like":0